summary: A temple added to the base of the shrine of Azura.
descriptionHtml:
This is a small mod I made for my game that adds a small temple at the base of the Azura shrine. I did not like how barren the area was. There are some pilgrims and temple priests in the area. Food, drink & alchemy ingredients are available. This also corrects some minor terrain errors in the vanilla game.

I recommend using NMM to load

No DLC's needed.

This mod has been cleaned & follower friendly.
